    "body": "I believe that you either mix up networks or your node isn't synced yet.\r\n\r\nInfura:\r\n\r\n```\r\n> curl --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"method\":\"eth_getBlockTransactionCountByHash\",\"params\":[\"0xeff0e1a88aa19ec53e5e1f9b3a4ea3dd897f037cc36c786712b93f0a197eb79c\"]}' https://mainnet.infura.io\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":\"0xac\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\nLocal node:\r\n```\r\n> curl --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"method\":\"eth_getBlockTransactionCountByHash\",\"params\":[\"0xeff0e1a88aa19ec53e5e1f9b3a4ea3dd897f037cc36c786712b93f0a197eb79c\"]}' localhost:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":\"0xac\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe block with the hash you pointed is block number 4297758 which is fairly recent. Ensure that your node has synced beyond that block number. If not geth will return null.",
